<tr>
<td colspan="3" class="boilerplate metadata" style="line-height:10pt; padding:0.5em;"><small><b>Note</b>: This page may contain <a href="/wiki/Help:IPA" title="Help:IPA" class="mw-redirect">IPA</a> phonetic symbols in <a href="/wiki/Unicode" title="Unicode">Unicode</a>.</small></td>
