<p><a name="Learning_courses.2Fresources" id="Learning_courses.2Fresources"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Lojban&amp;action=edit&amp;section=36" title="Edit section: Learning courses/resources">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Learning courses/resources</span></h3>
<p><a name="Beginner" id="Beginner"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Lojban&amp;action=edit&amp;section=37" title="Edit section: Beginner">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Beginner</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.coirodo.com/english/ctuca/01.html" class="external text" title="http://www.coirodo.com/english/ctuca/01.html" rel="nofollow">Conversational Lojban</a></li>
<li><a href="http://neptune.spaceports.com/~words/lojban.html" class="external text" title="http://neptune.spaceports.com/~words/lojban.html" rel="nofollow">Lojban: A Logical Language</a> by Robin Turner</li>
<li><a href="http://lojban.org/publications/level0/brochure/book1.html" class="external text" title="http://lojban.org/publications/level0/brochure/book1.html" rel="nofollow">What is Lojban?</a> by John Cowan and Nick Nicholas</li>
<li><a href="http://www.tlg.uci.edu/~opoudjis/lojbanbrochure/lessons/book1.html" class="external text" title="http://www.tlg.uci.edu/~opoudjis/lojbanbrochure/lessons/book1.html" rel="nofollow">Lojban For Beginners</a> by Robin Turner and Nick Nicholas</li>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=Everyday+Lojban+B01&amp;bl" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=Everyday+Lojban+B01&amp;bl" rel="nofollow">Everyday Lojban</a> by Lojban.org</li>
<li><a href="http://ptolemy.tlg.uci.edu/~opoudjis/lojbanbrochure/lessons/book1.html" class="external text" title="http://ptolemy.tlg.uci.edu/~opoudjis/lojbanbrochure/lessons/book1.html" rel="nofollow">Lojban Introductory Lessons</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/jboski/" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/jboski/" rel="nofollow">jboski</a>: an online Lojban-to-English translator by LLG</li>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=PARALLEL+2&amp;bl" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=PARALLEL+2&amp;bl" rel="nofollow">Parallel 2</a>: a free program for parallel reading and listening, based on the <a href="/w/index.php?title=Implicit_learning&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Implicit learning (page does not exist)">implicit learning approach</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=jMemorize+instructions&amp;bl" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=jMemorize+instructions&amp;bl" rel="nofollow">jMemorize</a>:</li>
<li><a href="http://www.digitalkingdom.org/~bjoern/Popup/" class="external text" title="http://www.digitalkingdom.org/~bjoern/Popup/" rel="nofollow">Popup.app</a>: a GNUstep based vocabulary learning tool that can use cmafi'e to extract the vocabulary from a given text.</li>
<li><a href="http://quizlet.com/group/152/" class="external text" title="http://quizlet.com/group/152/" rel="nofollow">Quizlet</a>:</li>
<li><a href="http://perpetuum-immobile.de/lojban_number.py" class="external text" title="http://perpetuum-immobile.de/lojban_number.py" rel="nofollow">Lojbanic Number Trainer</a>: a simple web tool</li>
<li><a href="http://xahlee.org/lojban/lojban.html" class="external text" title="http://xahlee.org/lojban/lojban.html" rel="nofollow">Xah's Logical Language Page</a>: A brief introduction + some word categories</li>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=Software+assisted+learning&amp;bl" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=Software+assisted+learning&amp;bl" rel="nofollow">Software Assisted Learning</a>: miscellaneous software listed on Lojban.org</li>
<li><a href="http://jbo.wikipedia.org/wiki/pixra_liste_loi_gismu" class="extiw" title="jbo:pixra liste loi gismu">Basic Lojban picture wordlist</a>: a list of picturable gismu on the Lojban Wikipedia</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Advanced" id="Advanced"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Lojban&amp;action=edit&amp;section=38" title="Edit section: Advanced">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Advanced</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/publications/wordlists/gismu.txt" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/publications/wordlists/gismu.txt" rel="nofollow">gimste</a>: a full list of Lojban gismu</li>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/publications/brochures/lojex.txt" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/publications/brochures/lojex.txt" rel="nofollow">Diagrammed Summary of Lojban Grammar Forms with Example Sentences</a> by LLG</li>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-download_wiki_attachment.php?attId=198&amp;page=The+Lojban+Reference+Grammar" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-download_wiki_attachment.php?attId=198&amp;page=The+Lojban+Reference+Grammar" rel="nofollow">The Lojban Reference Grammar</a> by John Cowan</li>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-download_wiki_attachment.php?attId=89" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-download_wiki_attachment.php?attId=89" rel="nofollow">The Level 0 Booklet</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/rational/library/2740.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/rational/library/2740.html" rel="nofollow">Using UML to understand Lojban</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/jbovlaste/" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/jbovlaste/" rel="nofollow">jbovlaste</a>: an official Lojban dictionary project</li>
</ul>
