<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=xirli%27u+selsanga&amp;bl" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=xirli%27u+selsanga&amp;bl" rel="nofollow">xirli'u selsanga</a>: a poem by Federico Garca Lorca, translated by xorxes</li>
