<li><a href="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=sipna+pemci&amp;bl" class="external text" title="http://www.lojban.org/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=sipna+pemci&amp;bl" rel="nofollow">sipna pemci</a>: by Arnt Richard Johansen</li>
<li><a href="http://www.fa-kuan.muc.de/LOJBAN.RXML" class="external text" title="http://www.fa-kuan.muc.de/LOJBAN.RXML" rel="nofollow">Lojban Poetry - Tengwar script</a>: by .aulun.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.fa-kuan.muc.de/HAIKU.RXML" class="external text" title="http://www.fa-kuan.muc.de/HAIKU.RXML" rel="nofollow">Lojban Haikus - Hiragana script</a>: by xorxes. &amp; .aulun.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.fa-kuan.muc.de/HAIKU2.RXML" class="external text" title="http://www.fa-kuan.muc.de/HAIKU2.RXML" rel="nofollow">Lojban Haikus - Hiragana script</a>: by .aulun.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.fa-kuan.muc.de/GOETHE.RXML" class="external text" title="http://www.fa-kuan.muc.de/GOETHE.RXML" rel="nofollow">Goethe: nicte selsa'a be le dzuli'u</a>: by .aulun.</li>
</ul>
